public class AddMoodActivity extends androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity
AddMoodActivity is responsible for allowing users to add a new mood entry. It provides functionality to select an emoji, add a reason, choose a group, and optionally upload an image. The mood data is then saved to Firestore.
Author:
Roshan Banisetti, Eric, Garrick
